"We may not have won the war," Tanis began, "but surely we have won<BR> a major battle--".<BR>
Raistlin coughed and shook his head sadly.<BR>
"Do you see hope?"<BR>
"Hope is the denial of reality.  It is the carrot dangled before the draft horse<BR> to keep him plodding along in a vain attempt to reach it."<BR>
"Are you saying we should just give up?" Tanis asked irritably.<BR>
"I'm saying we should remove the carrot and walk forward with our eyes<BR> open," Raistlin answered...<P><i></i></TD></TR><TR BGCOLOR=#CCCCCC><TD NOWRAP width=20% valign=top align=left><B><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ueayenaf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eayenaf</A></FONT></B><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Registered User</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>posts: </FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>5</FONT><BR><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>(</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>5/11/01</FONT> <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1 COLOR=#FF0000>1:05:41 pm</FONT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>)<BR></FONT></TD><TD VALIGN=TOP ALIGN=LEFT><B><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Re:  Ragefire spawns:  reservation/rotation list</font></B><HR><FONT SIZE=2 FACE="Verdana,Arial">Business is more than making financial decisions, it is also working with people -- often with people you don't know.  To run a business effectively and efficiently, you need training.  With that training, you would be able to determine whether the anonymous person was giving you sound advice or blowing smoke (although this would probably be the more likely case).  If you cannot trust yourself to listen to other people with good ideas, regardless of who they are, then you should not be the one leading these efforts -- you can't trust yourself to listen to others and still be able to make good decisions.  In the context of this discussion, this is not a business.  If it was a business, then can you honestly say that you have training for managing the people of this server?  Do you know what is best for everyone?<br>
<br>
If you would have said that you were going to remove people in the first place, then maybe we wouldn't be having this discussion at this point Fayenae.  A simple, &quot;I agree that they should be removed&quot; would have sufficed.  Why then did you drag this out?  Saying that people will be moved to the back of the list is one thing, removing them is another.  You had NOT previously said &quot;IF they get to Ragefire with no pearl they will be dropped and have to wait to get the pearl to get on the list.&quot;  What you did say was &quot;If you were to get to the top of the list and not have a pearl you would fall to the back&quot;.  If you want to convey a point, then be clear about it.  Falling to the back of the list is a completely different concept than removing people from the list.<br>
<br>
Lastly, what does &quot;NO ONE will be removed from the list&quot; mean?  Nobody will be removed from the list even if they still don't have a pearl in a month's time frame?  A month's time frame seems to be a poplular choice -- one that was suggested by someone else.  Is not a month's time frame enough for a player to fully demonstrate, using your words, &quot;A) really into doing [the quest], [and] B) capable of doing [the quest]&quot;?  Honesty and integrity may be virtues that you hold, but clear communication and logical thinking are not.</font><P><P><i><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ueayenaf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Eayenaf</A> at: 5/11/01 2:10:04 pm</FONT><br></i></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE><TABLE BORDER=0 WIDTH=95%><TR><TD ALIGN=LEFT><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Page</FONT>&nbsp; <FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>1</FONT>&nbsp; <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showMessageRange?topicID=587.topic&start=21&stop=24><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>2</FONT></a></TD><TD ALIGN=RIGHT> &nbsp;<A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showMessage?topicID=786.topic><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=1>Next Topic >></FONT></A> </TD></TR></TABLE><BR><TABLE WIDTH=95% BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=587.topic&index=279><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/gfx/addReply1.gif border=0></A></TD><TD><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.emailToFriend?topicID=587.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/images/email.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Email This To a Friend"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZE=2>&nbsp;Email This To a Friend</FONT><BR><A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/fluclin71335dragonsandtheplanes.threadControl?topicID=587.topic><IMG SRC=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/image/deleteThreadFire.gif BORDER=0 ALT="Topic Control Image"></A><FONT FACE="Verdana,Arial" SIZ